details.sectionContent: It is an event where you can enlighten your talent.
You got moves? Pretty awesome voice? Guitar? Drums? Show your talent over here and become Prakarsh 2018's SPOTLIGHT!
All the participants will show their talent, performing in 3 minutes (maximum). Setup time: - 2 minutes maximum.

The participants will be given 10-15 minutes to prepare on the task given to them. o They have to get ready with the given twist on time. Note: - Negative marking will be done if your performance is not within the time limit or you come late for the same
